<body>
<div><head>喪服變除圖</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.2">天子之子封為諸侯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.3">天子皆不服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.4">杜佑《通典》卷八十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.5">「天子弔三公及三孤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.6">弁絰錫縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.7">弔六卿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.8">弁絰錫縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.9">弔大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.10">弁絰疑縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.11">弔士，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.12">弁絰緦縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.13">弔畿內諸侯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.14">弁絰緦縗服。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.15">《通典》卷八十一引無「及三孤及六卿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.16">弁絰錫縗」句，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.17">士合大夫作「弔大夫士，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.18">皆弁絰疑縗。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-1a.19">据《太平御覽》卷五百六十一校正。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.2">「始聞喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.3">去吉冠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.4">著素弁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.5">十五升布深衣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.6">從其君哭太廟阼階下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.7">祖絻即位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.8">成踊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.9">襲絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.10">吉屨無絇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.11">張帷為次於其廳舍，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.12">別內外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.13">蔬食飲水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.14">牡麻絰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.15">至成服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.16">服四升半繐布縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.17">縷裳細而疏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.18">其冠八升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.19">纓帶中衣領袖緣亦如之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.20">七月而除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.21">受以朝服素冠。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.22">踰月復吉。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-2a.23">《通典》卷八十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.2">徐整問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.3">「諸侯之大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.4">時會見於天子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.5">故為繐縗七月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.6">不知此大夫時以何事而得見也？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.7">若遠國大夫在荒服者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.8">未嘗及見天子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.9">亦為服不？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.10">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.11">「諸侯之大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.12">有出朝聘之事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.13">會見天子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.14">故言時會。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.15">雖未會見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.16">猶服此服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.17">士已下則無服。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-3a.18">《通典》卷八十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.2">徐整問：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.3">「為姑姊長殤在大功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.4">下殤在小功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.5">為姊已下絻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.6">五六歲未成童子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.7">為父母不杖不廬不菲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.8">至重猶尚不備。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.9">今此何以越得為姊殤服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.10">備大功小功之制乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.11">十七八尚可，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.12">恐六七歲兒未能服此縗麻。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.13">慈答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.14">「六七歲雖未成童，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.15">其姊死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.16">故宜著布深衣。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.17">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.18">又卷內引庾蔚之說「射慈以為未八歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-4a.19">服其近屬布深衣」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.2">「諸侯之女為天子后，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.3">為天子之親服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.4">隨天王而降一等。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.5">諸侯之女為后，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.6">為其父母及兄弟為夫後者服𪗋縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.7">其宗子亦不降。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.8">徐整云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.9">「諸侯女嫁為天子后，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.10">為外親尊同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.11">則如邦人為君之長子三年也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-5a.12">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.2">徐整問云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.3">「經言為夫人、君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.4">不道為其妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.5">然則公卿諸侯之妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.6">不為皇后服耶？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.7">答云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.8">「皇后，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.9">天下之母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.10">則宜服周。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.11">禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.12">君命其夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.13">后夫人亦宜命其婦。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.14">其受命，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.15">則不宜無服。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-6a.16">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.2">「夫為妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.3">去吉冠。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.4">大夫以上素弁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.5">士素委貌。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.6">衣十五升白布深衣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.7">吉屨無絇。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.8">尸襲之時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.9">亦哭踊。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-7a.10">《通典》卷八十四。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.2">「為父既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.3">日中反哭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.4">諸侯於太祖廟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.5">別子為卿大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.6">亦於太祖廟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.7">其非別子為卿大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.8">於皇考廟中士、下士於王考廟。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.9">皆升自西階，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.10">東西哭踊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.11">虞祭於殯宮。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-8a.12">《通典》卷八十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.2">「繼母為廬當就繼母之家。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.3">若遠不得往者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.4">則別為異室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.5">亦有廬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.6">變除堊室及禫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.7">如親子也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.8">亦報子周。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.9">不言報者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.10">凡經中之文悉報也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-9a.11">《通典》卷八十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.2">徐整問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.3">「出妻之子為其母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.4">及父卒繼母嫁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.5">為之服、報，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.6">皆周也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.7">二母既出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.8">則為絕族。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.9">今子為之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.10">皆當於何處為位？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.11">有廬堊室不？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.12">出母亦當報其子不繼母報子於何處制服？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.13">豈止所適者之家為哭位乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.14">又當有禫不？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.15">射慈答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.16">「堂就出母之家。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.17">若遠不得往者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.18">可別為異室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.19">亦有廬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.20">變除、堊室及禫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.21">如親子也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.22">母亦報子周也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-10a.23">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.2">徐整問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.3">「婦人為君服周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.4">則諸侯夫人亦為天子服此也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.5">其聞喪之儀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.6">衣麻之數，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.7">哭泣之位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.8">變除之節，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.9">如周制將復有異耶？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.10">射慈答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.11">「其畿內諸侯夫人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.12">有助祭之禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.13">則始喪之時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.14">悉當到京師，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.15">復當還耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.16">其畿外諸侯聞喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.17">則當於路寢庭發喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.18">夫人當堂上也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.19">變除之節，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.20">皆如周服之制也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-11a.21">《通典》卷九十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.2">徐整問射慈曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.3">「八歲以上為殤者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.4">服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.5">未滿八歲為無服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.6">假令子以元年正月生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.7">七歲十二月死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.8">此為七歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.9">則無服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.10">或以元年十二月生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.11">以八年正月死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.12">以但踐八年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.13">計其日月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.14">適六歲耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.15">然號為八歲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.16">日月甚少；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.17">全七歲者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.18">日月為多。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.19">若人有二子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.20">各死如此，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.21">其七歲者獨無服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.22">則父母之恩有偏頗。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.23">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.24">「凡制數自以生月計之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.25">不以歲也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.26">問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.27">「無服之殤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.28">以日易月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.29">哭之於何處？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.30">有位無？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.31">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.32">「哭之無位。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.33">禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.34">葬下殤於園中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.35">則無服之殤亦於園也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.36">其哭之就圍也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-12a.37">《通典》卷九十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.2">徐整問射慈云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.3">「子思哭嫂為位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.4">在何面加麻袒絻為位？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.5">不審服此有日數乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.6">慈答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.7">「凡喪位皆西面。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.8">此麻者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.9">謂大殮及殯之時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.10">已畢而釋之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-13a.11">《通典》卷九十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.2">徐整問射慈曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.3">「古者三十而娶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.4">何緣當服得夫之姊殤服？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.5">經文特為士作，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.6">若說國君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.7">皆別言君若公。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.8">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.9">「三十而娶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.10">禮之常制也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.11">古者七十而傳宗事與子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.12">年雖幼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.13">未滿三十，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.14">自得少娶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.15">故曾子問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.16">『宗子雖七十，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.17">無無主婦。』<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.18">此言宗子巳老傳宗事與子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.19">則宜有主婦。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-14a.20">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.2">「諸侯之女為諸侯夫人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.3">服諸侯之親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.4">隨諸侯降一等，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.5">還為族親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.6">則皆降之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.7">《通典》卷九十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.8">「傳曰『尊同則得服其親服』。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.9">言尊同者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.10">謂俱為卿大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.11">各隨本親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.12">則不降也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.13">諸侯女為諸侯夫人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.14">不降父母、昆弟之為父後者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.15">大夫妻唯父母、昆弟為父後者、宗子不降也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-15a.16">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a" ed="CHANT" n="001-16a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.2">閒傳：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.3">「斬縗之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.4">既虞卒哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.5">遭𪗋縗之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.6">輕者包，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.7">重者特。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.8">斬縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.9">既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.10">縗裳六升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.11">男子絰帶悉易以葛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.12">婦人易首絰以葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.13">腰帶故麻也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.14">但就五分去一分，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.15">殺小之耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.16">仍遭母及伯叔兄𪗋縗之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.17">其為母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.18">更以四升布為腰帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.19">謂之包，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.20">言以包斬縗帶也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.21">絰斬縗之葛絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.22">謂之重者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.23">主於尊也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.24">婦人易首絰以麻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.25">亦謂之包；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.26">帶斬縗之麻帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.27">謂之特。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.28">周喪既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.29">服上服六升之縗裳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.30">男子帶上服之葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.31">婦人絰上服之葛絰也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-16a.32">《通典》卷九十七引射慈。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a" ed="CHANT" n="001-17a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.2">服重者則易輕者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.3">「𪗋縗之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.4">既虞卒哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.5">遭大功之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.6">麻葛兼服之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.7">𪗋縗既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.8">為母七升正服縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.9">八升絰帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.10">悉葛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.11">婦人首絰以葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.12">腰帶故麻也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.13">亦猶五分去一，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.14">殺小之耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.15">又遭大功之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.16">更制大功之喪縗裳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.17">男子以麻為腰帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.18">絰周之葛絰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.19">婦人易首絰以麻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.20">帶周之葛帶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.21">大功既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.22">亦服其功縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.23">男子婦人悉反著周喪既葬之絰帶也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-17a.24">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a" ed="CHANT" n="001-18a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.2">服問：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.3">「三年之喪既練矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.4">有期之喪既葬矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.5">則帶其故葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.6">絰期之絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.7">服其功縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.8">謂三年既練縗七升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.9">男子首絰、婦人麻帶俱已徐矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.10">又遭周喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.11">更制周縗裳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.12">絰帶悉麻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.13">周喪既畢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.14">為母縗七升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.15">正服縗八升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.16">義服縗九升，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.17">謂之功縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.18">男子帶綀之葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.19">絰周之麻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.20">謂既葬之麻也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.21">其大四寸百二十五分之七十六也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-18a.22">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a" ed="CHANT" n="001-19a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.2">「既練，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.3">遭大功喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.4">麻葛重者既練，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.5">男子有葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.6">婦人有葛絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.7">男子首絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.8">婦人麻帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.9">俱已除矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.10">又遭大功之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.11">亦更制縗裳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.12">絰帶皆麻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.13">謂之重麻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.14">大功既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.15">還服練縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.16">男子帶練之葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.17">絰周之葛絰；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.18">其婦人絰其練葛絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.19">帶周之葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.20">謂之重葛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.21">〈檀弓〉曰『婦人不葛帶』，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.22">謂𪗋斬之婦人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.23">今此帶周之葛帶者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.24">大功既葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.25">婦人得葛帶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.26">不服大功之葛帶而帶周之葛帶者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.27">斬縗既練，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.28">婦人除葛絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.29">大功五寸二十五分之十九，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.30">若帶大功之葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.31">裁大三寸六百二十五分寸之四百二十九，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.32">分絰帶五分去一之差也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.33">故帶周之葛帶。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.34">周之葛帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.35">大四寸百二十五分寸之七十六，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.36">與練首絰差之宜也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.37">男子不絰大功葛絰而絰周之葛絰者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.38">亦以非練帶之差也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-19a.39">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a" ed="CHANT" n="001-20a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.2">服問曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.3">「殤長中變三年之葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.4">終殤之月算而反三年之葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.5">是非重麻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.6">為其無卒哭之稅。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.7">下殤則不。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.8">「謂大功之親為殤在小功緦麻者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.9">皆易縗葛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.10">著麻絰帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.11">以終殤之月數，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.12">而反三年之葛。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.13">謂若從父昆弟、絰、庶孫之長殤、中殤在小功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.14">婦人為夫叔又長殤在小功、中殤在緦麻者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.15">此殤麻亦斷本。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.16">變三年之葛者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.17">正親親也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.18">下殤不言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.19">賤也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-20a.20">《通典》卷九十七引射慈。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a" ed="CHANT" n="001-21a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.2">〈檀弓〉：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.3">「有遠兄弟之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.4">雖緦必往。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.5">非兄弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.6">雖鄰不往。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.7">「雖緦必往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.8">親骨肉也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.9">雖鄰不往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.10">疏無親也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-21a.11">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a" ed="CHANT" n="001-22a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.2">「士為姑姊妹女子子適人與主者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.3">𪗋縗周。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.4">《通典》卷九十九引吳射慈。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.5">「三年、周喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.6">歲沒閏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.7">九月以下數閏也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.8">《通典》卷一百引射慈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-22a.9">又王儉引鄭、射、王、賀唯云「閏則沒閏」。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a" ed="CHANT" n="001-23a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.2">徐整問射慈曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.3">「改葬緦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.4">其奠如大斂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.5">從廟之廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.6">從墓望墓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.7">禮宜同也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.8">又此大斂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.9">謂始死之大斂耶？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.10">從廟悉謂何廟？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.11">牲物何用？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.12">慈答：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.13">「奠如大斂奠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.14">士大斂特豚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.15">從禰廟朝祖廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.16">從故墓之新墓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.17">皆用特豚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.18">大夫以上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.19">其禮亡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.20">以此推之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.21">大夫奠用特豚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.22">天子太牢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.23">諸侯少牢。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-23a.24">《通典》卷一百二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a" ed="CHANT" n="001-24a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.2">徐整問改葬虞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.3">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.4">「不在殯宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.5">又不為位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.6">何虞之有。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.7">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.8">徐整間射慈曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.9">「久喪不除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.10">小祥練可知爾。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.11">有故未得葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.12">遂至二十八月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.13">服制己過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.14">可得變不？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.15">豈服十年五年至葬乃止乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.16">答曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.17">「生雖不得變，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.18">其餘旁親亦不除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.19">日月竟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.20">自釋之耳。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-24a.21">《通典》卷一百三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a" ed="CHANT" n="001-25a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.2">《禮記》：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.3">「女子十五而笄。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.4">射慈云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.5">「十九猶為殤。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.6">《南史‧江謐傳》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.7">〈檀弓〉曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.8">「麌而立尸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.9">有几筵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.10">卒哭而諱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.11">生事畢而鬼事始已。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.12">下室之饋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.13">器物几杖如平生。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1081_CHANT_001-25a.14">《禮記‧檀弓正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
